OL,3,CTrio to be deported after serving
OL,4,Cchild grooming sentences
OL,6,FThree asylum seekers who groomed and
OL,7,Fsexually abused a teenage girl will be
OL,8,Fdeported after serving their prison
OL,9,Fsentences, a court has heard.
OL,11,FHamdulluh Hamdadd, 24, met the 16-year-
OL,12,Fold girl at a shop in Hull before
OL,13,Fgiving her gifts and introducing her
OL,14,Fto fellow Afghan nationals, 20-year
OL,15,Fold Rafiullah Naseri and Amjid
OL,16,FAkakhail, 22.
OL,18,FThey plied her with alcohol and drugs
OL,19,Fand gave her money as they abused her
OL,20,Fat addresses across Hull.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
