OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782823737
OL,3,CTrio to be deported after serving
OL,4,Cchild grooming sentences
OL,6,FAll three were found guilty following
OL,7,Fa trial at Hull Crown Court of child
OL,8,Fsexual exploitation charges.
OL,10,FHamdadd, of Park Grove in Hull, who
OL,11,Falso admitted possessing extreme
OL,12,Fpornography and making an indecent
OL,13,Fphotograph, was jailed for eight years.
OL,15,FNaseri, of Spring Bank in Hull,
OL,16,Freceived the same sentence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
