CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782823737
OL,3,CTrio to be deported after serving
OL,4,Cchild grooming sentences
OL,6,FAkakhail, of Pearson Street in
OL,7,FWakefield, also pleaded guilty at an
OL,8,Fearlier court hearing to making an
OL,9,Findecent photograph of a child. He was
OL,10,Fjailed for four years.
OL,12,FAs well as facing deportation once
OL,13,Fthey are released, all three men were
OL,14,Fgiven lifetime restraining orders and
OL,15,Fplaced on the Sex Offenders Register
OL,16,Findefinitely.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
