OL,3,CTrio to be deported after serving
OL,4,Cchild grooming sentences
OL,6,FDet Supt Nicole Elliott, of Humberside
OL,7,FPolice, said: "This case represents a
OL,8,Fharrowing example of grooming,
OL,9,Fmanipulation and predatory behaviour
OL,10,Fby three men who deliberately targeted
OL,11,Fa vulnerable child.
OL,13,F"They offered money, alcohol and
OL,14,Fdrugs, using these tactics to gain
OL,15,Fcontrol before sexually abusing her
OL,16,Ffor their own gratification.
OL,18,F"The victim has shown remarkable
OL,19,Fcourage and strength in extremely
OL,20,Ftraumatic circumstances."
